

/* Experimental function Vi. Calling Vi with a function name will
 * result in editing the file the function is defined in (according
 * to the .def file). Calling Vi with a file name will edit the
 * file. The editor used is vi.
 */

10 # Vi(_what)_(FindFunction(what)!="") <--
   SystemCall("vi +/":what:" ":FindFile(FindFunction(what)));
20 # Vi(_what)_(FindFile(what) != "")   <--
   SystemCall("vi ":FindFile(what));

